lead_paragraph: Because of an editing error, an Associated Press report in some editions of the college basketball roundup last Sunday carried an incorrect label. Arizona State defeated Washington State, 76-35, in women’s basketball — not men’s. (On the same day, the Washington State men defeated Arizona State in overtime, 51-49.).
